---
title: Southwest-Style Grilled Steak and Shrimp with Sweet Potatoes and Fresh Herb Mayo
description: Grilled steak and herby foil-pouch shrimp make the perfect pair in this Southwestern-inspired feast! Dip and drizzle everything with delicious herb mayo!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crevettes-et-steaks-grilles-a-la-sud-ouest-e7e2a327.jpg
